    <title>Gain과 Fader의 근본적인 차이는 무엇인가 어떻게 결정하는가</title>
    <link>https://berom.net/Articles/Gain%EA%B3%BC-Fader%EC%9D%98-%EA%B7%BC%EB%B3%B8%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EB%8A%94-%EB%AC%B4%EC%97%87%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%80-%EC%96%B4%EB%96%BB%EA%B2%8C-%EA%B2%B0%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%EA%B0%80</link>
